  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_04_07: Rabbi Ishmael his son said: he who refrains himself from judgment, rids himse...",
  "body": "Rabbi Ishmael his son said: he who refrains himself from judgment, rids himself of enmity, robbery and false swearing; But he whose heart is presumptuous in giving a judicial decision, is foolish, wicked and arrogant.",
